Class Dog

  • java.lang.Object
    • animals.Pet
      • animals.Dog

  • public class Dog
extends Pet

    Contains dog attributes and algorithms to modify the attributes. Considered a Pet.

    Depends on:

    • Pet

    Dog - a domesticated carnivorous mammal that typically has a long snout, an acute sense of smell, nonretractable claws, and a barking, howling, or whining voice.
